channel.title: Comments on: Warcraft Night Elves have an Attitude Problem

item.title: By: Hyd
item.dc:creator: Hyd
item.description: There's a warrior trainer in SW that makes some smartass crack when you click on him as a hunter. "Run away little boy, before you get hurt," or something like that. You don't get to say to him, "Funny, I didn't see _your_ mangy ass with me in Southshore getting jacked up by Horde last night."
